        <abstract>
          <para>
            This document is intended to become a complete reference manual for 
            GPE application development. At the point of starting this we have 
            various sources of information about the wisdom how to create or 
            continue a GPE application. In the past years we have been collecting 
            lots of experience in coding for handhelds devices - it is very 
            important not only to share the software but the experience that lead 
            to this software as well.
          </para>
